{"tid":1306601,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老味你地槍口對外得唔撚得呀","createTime":"2019-07-11T08:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T19:13:38.000Z","uid":259736,"like":39,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1b1fcc91c38cd5bd4d23d602d0dba99198414725","tid":1306601,"uid":259736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:13:17.000Z","msg":"個撚個係度屌自己友on9！兄弟爬山呀！<br />\n被人打果個又唔撚係你，個撚個係度做鍵盤戰士。<br />\n我知你地為硬淨巴好，心痛佢，但人地咁大個人知自己做緊咩架啦，你地係屌人on9知唔知好撚影響士氣呀，專心留力屌個肥佬啦！<br />\n如果當日我地發夢衝立法會後第二日個個係咁屌我地on9既話你又會點諗？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全力屌個死肥佬呀你班撚樣</span><br />\n<br />\n另外如果硬淨巴打睇到呢個post既我想為香港同你講聲多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d9c591c87620c0c787dbad7863c9e7f8bd7a15","tid":1306601,"uid":131843,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:18:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>所有屌過人唔還手既<br />\n同我出去用兩倍力度屌返個肥佬<br />\n用返同樣時間幫手將藍絲暴力唱通街先好再出聲</strong></span></span><br />\n你老味有勁多人，睇住佢用晒啲精神時間，<br />\n用足半日時間秒回post黎全力屌自己人"},{"pid":"44555214e63f47a3ac114395e5a6789f5736a935","tid":1306601,"uid":276191,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:26:56.000Z","msg":"硬淨巴, 你好嘢<br />\n並不是有勇無謀<br />\n而是忍辱負重<br />\n你已經為大家吃了太多苦<br />\n都唔知點多謝你好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72d41d400b44e5ec8e1c6e055d18eb3135b86cfb","tid":1306601,"uid":189799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:28:42.000Z","msg":"無撚錯，完全無人撚個藍絲。留意番，仲未起到佢底呀!!!"},{"pid":"3e20a2f91abe00758205d457dcca761fe59fd2fd","tid":1306601,"uid":104171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4d9c591c87620c0c787dbad7863c9e7f8bd7a15","tid":1306601,"uid":131843,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:18:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong